headline: Dominion Energy (D) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Dominion Energy (D) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +13.98% and +8.03%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
